item.title: Service Catalog Factory
item.description: Select the pre-configured CloudFormation Template Service Catalog Factory can be installed via a pre-created AWS CloudFormation template stored in Amazon S3. There are many configuration options for you to customise your installation. For this workshop we will be using the following quick link which has the settings already preconfigured for you: Create the initialisation stack Check the box labeled “I acknowledge that AWS CloudFormation might create IAM resources with custom names.
